Upon creating an account in StandupTime, you will invite users and add them to a team. Within the team’s settings you will set the Daily Standup Meetings Time and Days it will happen(i.e. Monday, Wednesday, Friday at 10AM).  Everytime the meeting is set to occur, an email will be sent with a link to Add that day’s tasks, complete(re: check­off) yesterday's tasks, and add any impediments the team member may be experiencing. After the meeting has occurred an automated email recapping everyone’s standup submission will be sent to all team members. Headquarters Regions: Greater San Diego Area, West Coast, Western US
Full Description: We are a unique dental office that is committed to our patient's total health and wellness. It is our goal to educate our patients about their oral condition and give  them the opportunity to achieve or maintain optimal oral health. In addition to general dental care, we offer many specialized services such as same day crowns, Same Day Smiles, sedation dentistry, and all-in-one dental implant treatment. Dr. Scott and Dr. Leslie both have extensive training in aesthetic smile design and can customize a plan based on what the patient would like to achieve. We utilize the latest in digital dental technology including digital x-rays and 3D imaging to aide in complete diagnosis.
